Use the standard library
This is how to multiply of a and b:
   Remember that sa is tostring of a
   Remember that sb is tostring of b
   Remember that na is sa's length
   Remember that nb is sb's length
   Remember that i is 0
   Remember that total is 0
   Do this na times:
      Remember that ca is item i in sa
      Remember that da is diff of ca and 48
      Remember that j is 0
      Do this nb times:
         Remember that cb is item j in sb
         Remember that db is diff of cb and 48
         Remember that total is sum of total and (product of da and db)
         Increase j
      End do
      Increase i
   End do
   The answer is total
Now you know
>>> multiply of 148 and 412
16
>>> multiply of 19 and 28
72
>>> multiply of 2020 and 1851
0